OL,3,CWhy travel and food supplies to the
OL,4,CIsles of Scilly have been halted
OL,6,FTravel and the delivery of food
OL,7,Fsupplies to the Isles of Scilly have
OL,8,Fbeen halted because of broken vessels
OL,9,Fand bad weather.
OL,11,FThe Isles of Scilly steamship group
OL,12,Fsays travel will cease until Monday 13
OL,13,FApril because of a technical issue on
OL,14,Fpassenger ferry Scillonian III and
OL,15,F"deteriorating weather conditions".
OL,17,FEarlier this week, its freight ship
OL,18,Fcould not deliver supplies because of
OL,19,Fissues with its crane and compass.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
