OL,3,CWhy travel and food supplies to the
OL,4,CIsles of Scilly have been halted
OL,6,FGeorge Kershaw, who works at Castle
OL,7,FFarm Shop has already seen the impact
OL,8,Fof the delays.
OL,10,F"The bread has already gone because
OL,11,Fpeople were already aware that the
OL,12,Fboat wasn't going to sail, so the
OL,13,Fbread sold pretty quickly.
OL,15,F"We are running very low on milk, once
OL,16,Fthe bread and milks gone it will be
OL,17,Four fresh fruit and vegetables."
OL,19,FHe went on to explain how this is not
OL,20,Fa rare occurrence.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
