PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1776077823
OL,3,CWhy travel and food supplies to the
OL,4,CIsles of Scilly have been halted
OL,6,F"My other side of business I fit
OL,7,Fcarpets and unfortunately i've had to
OL,8,Fcancel several jobs this winter
OL,9,Fbecause I could get carpets over to
OL,10,Fthe islands which is a loss of
OL,11,Fthousands of pounds."
OL,13,FSamantha Mallon who is a resident on
OL,14,Fthe island says: "A lot of people self
OL,15,Fcater and if you can't even get the
OL,16,Fbasics to rustle up a meal, you know,
OL,17,Fpeople aren't expecting caviar and
OL,18,Ffrogs legs or anything exotic but if
OL,19,Fyou can't get a bag of carrots and
OL,20,Fpotatoes and a joint of meat, its not
OL,21,Fgood enough."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
