OL,3,CWhy travel and food supplies to the
OL,4,CIsles of Scilly have been halted
OL,6,FStuart Reid, CEO of Isles of Scilly
OL,7,FSteamship Group has explained how the
OL,8,FScillonian III is currently in the
OL,9,Fprocess of being fixed, whilst
OL,10,Fsailings over the weekend have been
OL,11,Fcancelled due to weather conditions.
OL,13,F"We would never put our passengers,
OL,14,Fcrew, or vessels at risk, as safety
OL,15,Fremains our top priority.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
