PN,43805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1776077823
OL,3,CWhy travel and food supplies to the
OL,4,CIsles of Scilly have been halted
OL,6,F"Our freight vessels, Gry Maritha and
OL,7,FGugh, are scheduled to resume sailings
OL,8,Fon Monday as the weather eases,
OL,9,Fcarrying further fresh produce.
OL,10,FScillonian III will also return to
OL,11,Fservice, transporting both passengers
OL,12,Fand freight.
OL,14,F"Whilst we acknowledge that this
OL,15,Fwinter's weather has been
OL,16,Funprecedented and that we have
OL,17,Fexperienced technical issues with our
OL,18,Fvessels, we have continued to maintain
OL,19,Ffreight services throughout.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
